Package TC

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    background
    Side-scrolling background class that makes it look like the player is progressing through the map.
    bossair
    Class for enemy bosses that move in the air
    bossground
    Class for a boss enemy that moves on the ground.
    bullet
    A weapon that the player uses to attack enemies.
    drawingpanel
    This acts just like JPanel, but it is tailored more for our game.
    enemybullet
    An enemy can shoot the player using an enemy bullet.
    enemyground
    A type of enemy that attacks on the ground.
    enemytank
    A type of enemy that attacks in the air.
    Framework
    The class that provides the basis for the whole game.
    game
    The class that provides the mechanics for the whole game.
    playertank
    This is the tank that the player will be controlling.
    powerup
    Defeated enemies will drop powerups at random times and the player can pick these up to gain an extra superpower.
    superpower
    Player is able to use a superpower, in which it wipes out all enemies currently on the map.
    updatescore
    Class that updates the high score of the game if the player's score happens to be bigger than the current high score.
    Window
    The main for our game.
